data.description: Possibility for dual living in this 4 bed 3 full bath home in SE Salem. Recent renovations include tile flooring in baths, new carpet in all bedrooms, interior paint, all 3 baths have been remodeled. Spacious fenced backyard with patio and deck, and a front deck for entertaining with a view off kitchen! Two cozy brick fireplaces. Basement is fully finished with a full bath and there are no steps to enter from garage to basement level. Great established Southeast Salem neighborhood, on a quiet cul-de-sac.
